Name: Running Education
About the game: Running Education -Different traps -Different environmental designs -Quick reflexes -Quality graphics -Simple gameplay -If you die in traps, you start over -You gotta go through it in one go without getting caught in the traps -We made 20 difficult tracks from each other -Some pitfalls can help you pass the level Are you good enough to overcome obstacles? You can only get our character out of the time impasse. You need to choose the right doors. We put in small hints for the right doors. If you see the hints, you can skip to the next level. You will be sent to different ipmasse of time. Your choices will bring you home but how soon where you can go is up to you. Remember, only you can find the house. We hope to welcome you at home You can get rid of the time impasse as soon as possible. Good luck because you'll need luck.
